body.name: Lilo and Stitch Packing Cubes - 5 Piece Packing Cube Set - Travel Essential - Disney Travel Packing Cubes 5 Piece Set
deliveryMessages: FREE delivery February 21 - 23 on orders shipped by Amazon over $35
features: Lilo and Stitch: Each case is embellished with the beloved and iconic Lilo and Stitch design, making it not just functional, but an irresistibly cute accessory for both kids and adults alike.

Packing Cube Case Set: This Lilo and Stitch packing cube set comes with five different sizes - extra large, large, medium, and small - making it ideal for all your packing and organizing needs. Large 13 X 18 X 5.5. Medium 12 X 16 X 5.5. Small 11 X 13 X 5.5. Flat Pouch 6 X 10.

Officially Licensed Disney Merchandise: Officially licensed Lilo and Stitch 5 piece packing cube case set. It features high-quality graphics that make it the perfect gift for back to school, camp, any accomplishment, Halloween, Christmas or birthday.

Organization Made Easy: The varying sizes of the cubes make it easy to organize your belongings, so you can quickly find what you need without digging through your suitcase. These packing cubes can be used for travel, home storage, or as a gift. They are versatile and perfect for organizing clothing, toiletries, cosmetics, and more.

Quality Construction: Made from sturdy and durable material that can withstand the rigors of travel. Its solid construction protects your cosmetics from being crushed or damaged. Featuring an easy-to-clean interior lining, these cases help you keep spills and stains contained and make cleanup a breeze.
